{"tid":1681001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左連錢都滿足唔到自己","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:11:02.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9882ea8d4c6ef42305ff0117a4d7285a0242b54c","tid":1681001,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"好想呃自己<br />\n用錢黎推動自己<br />\n買唔起都要租私樓<br />\n但重點唔係呢樣<br />\n原來自己一直在意唔係身外物<br />\n只係想搞好塊面<br />\n身高已成定局<br />\n可以你會話<br />\n揾到錢咪做facial<br />\n磨皮填凹凸洞<br />\n但點都彌補唔到天生<br />\n有d人天生就皮膚靚<br />\nd女使幾多錢美白<br />\n都唔及天生肌膚勝雪<br />\n白到隻豬咁個d女<br />\n人生有太多定局<br />\n有時都好憎自己搞塊面<br />\n但唔搞又肉酸<br />\n但搞左仲肉酸<br />\n呢個世界真係睇樣"},{"pid":"f17e2e8c60f8421f874b9c23c53fad0b58caf98f","tid":1681001,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40619e6cab99d302a327bf9a54139a9eda13e86","tid":1681001,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"}]}